{"tid":2061841,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[警世］當ex搵番你嘅時候","createTime":"2020-06-12T16:29:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-12T18:37:11.000Z","uid":244311,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4f77bb15378ceafdc713318d68bfddfba980bc7d","tid":2061841,"uid":244311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T16:29:32.000Z","msg":"話說Ex早排wts我話掛住我想搵番我做朋友<br />\n我開頭都打咗個突<br />\n然後就好想好想鬧柒佢<br />\n因為當初係佢話淡咗提分手先<br />\n但係我衰在對佢仲有些少留戀而鬧唔出口<br />\n<br />\n如是者我哋都wts咗一段時間聯絡番感情<br />\n當我滿心期待諗住約番佢出街嘅時候<br />\n佢至同我講話又冇咗感覺想斷聯<br />\n我真係覺得自己好撚賤<br />\n最後都係自己一廂情願<br />\n<br />\n所以大家有時真係唔好咁容易拎啲感情出黎<br />\n尤其係對ex<br />\n如果唔係到最後抽離唔到嗰個只會係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999"},{"pid":"99e487a65364389c0cb3309ae24d635bf94a4307","tid":2061841,"uid":254376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T16:30:53.000Z","msg":"臭雞中出即飛啦"},{"pid":"cedb67a7b2c732836722e4307d936b4450279d0f","tid":2061841,"uid":203701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T16:31:26.000Z","msg":"女人係咁㗎啦"},{"pid":"5d4e924c2bf27b7079fb7fbbb463e3d4d919eb64","tid":2061841,"uid":310059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T16:32:41.000Z","msg":"似係當你水泡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定係你做咗人地隻兵 自己唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d769d2d21215c6a9aecb0e4336141d1656b99f2","tid":2061841,"uid":349439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T16:37:25.000Z","msg":"所以大家有時真係唔好<del>咁容易拎啲感情出黎</del><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">FF太多</span></strong>"},{"pid":"df919bf374ae718e958b8f58cc2fa9eb3b49b6d8","tid":2061841,"uid":244311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T16:41:49.000Z","msg":"Too young too simple<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0